    "description_long": "This is a compact, black submachine gun with a boxy, utilitarian design, reminiscent of the iconic MAC-10. The weapon features a short, cylindrical barrel with a simple muzzle and a prominent rectangular receiver. A folding metal wire stock is attached to the rear, designed for compact storage and rapid deployment. The magazine is a straight, detachable box type, inserted vertically into the grip. The top of the receiver has a basic iron sight system, with a rear notch and a front post. The overall finish is matte black, with visible screws, pins, and a charging handle on the side.",
